{"tid":881232,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【擔心變父女戀】北大女生等放學 馬浚偉介意自己年紀大","createTime":"2018-10-29T09:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T13:11:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a06d37b1ca75dc4c2151484ffffa108f7f06bb","tid":881232,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20181029/s00009/767715b1f3debfd56165b544a1022656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20181029%2Fs00009%2F767715b1f3debfd56165b544a1022656.jpg&h=635ac3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬浚偉（馬仔）為香港開電視主持實況節目《同理‧繼續走》，昨晚於他成長的深水埗玩busking，並邀請部份節目受訪者出席，包括唐氏綜合症患者及家屬、跨性別人士等，在現場分享故事，吸引逾百名街坊圍觀。香港開電視高層更到場打氣，並為馬仔補祝47歲生日。<br />\n<br />\n馬仔指今年生日並無大肆慶祝，都是拜祭亡母、返教會，與家人及同事一齊食飯，簡簡單單慶祝。身形清減不少的馬仔自爆上個月曾入院，他說：「我轉食全齋3個多月，上個月突然血壓升得很高便入院，醫生說可能食齋影響荷爾蒙，身體需要調節，現在已無大礙且非常輕盈。」他形容近年比以前開放，不再抑鬱，有重生感覺，面對人群亦克服恐驚恐症。<br />\n<br />\n提到最近在北京大學進修，馬仔笑稱有不少北大女學生等他放學，暗示自己受異性歡迎，可是介意自己年紀大，擔心似「父女戀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1540803713599&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1540803713599%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181029&d=KTBDpI4eu99qGD55MLZpZjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5fcfa9bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1540803713599%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20181029&h=8234d072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1540803713599&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20181029</a>"},{"pid":"0ebfcd5c9be1c452c0c06c5e63e8e16f1b421188","tid":881232,"uid":156652,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZAjE8N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZAjE8N.gif&h=1d2014ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid